Mist::Menus
=========================

INSTALLATION

You should first install: 

  1. perl-SDL http://search.cpan.org/~jtpalmer/SDL-2.535/ or higher
  2. Color-Scheme http://search.cpan.org/~ian/Color-Scheme-1.02/lib/Color/Scheme.pm
  3. A true type font such as DejaVuSans.ttf
  4. Modify line 60(ish) of MistMenus to point to your font
      font   => '/path/fontname.ttf',

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

